  {
    title: 'Morrin Centre Interactive Archive',
    slug: 'morrin-centre',
    featured: true,
    description: 'An interactive Webflow-based archive experience designed for touch-screen use, allowing users to explore historical records through advanced filters, categories, years, and alphabetic search. The project combines a bold editorial interface with app-like database logic powered by Xano, bilingual support, light/dark mode, and custom interactions designed to make research feel intuitive, visual, and engaging.',
    credit: 'Webflow development by Tito Solano as part of Uroboro.ca development team.',
